@node Main "X_Next - Documentation"

                              'X_Next' 1.1

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'X_Next' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} in which you have to move to all
the tiles that are shown on the game board. You can move on any
tile except those that are immediately next, either horizontally,
vertically or diagonally, to your position. As you leave a tile, it
disappears, if a number is on it, that number will decrease by one.
When a board is completed, X_Next displays a new board and the game
continues...

  Have fun!

